======================================================================
RELATIONSHIP: W WORPITZKY <-> F WORPITZKY
======================================================================
W(T,r) = sum_P prod(r + s_e)
F(T,x) = sum_P x^{fwd(P)}
Relationship: W(T,r) = sum_k F_k (r+1/2)^k (r-1/2)^{n-1-k}


